ine Goyder</strong> [18:55]</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ze763kgrWGg\">Bringing Your Full Voice to Life</a> -  by <strong>Barbara McAfee</strong> [19:07]</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=80UVjkcxGmA\">How I Overcame My Fear of Public Speaking</a> -  by <strong>Danish Dhamani</strong> [08:36]</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eIho2S0ZahI\">How to speak so that people want to listen</a> -  by <strong>Julian Treasure</strong> [09:58]</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"websites\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#websites\" aria-label=\"websites permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Websites</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://speaking.io\">Speaking.io</a> - Tips for preparing your talk and get ready to deliver it</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JanVanRyswyck/awesome-talks\">awesome-talks</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/JanVanRyswyck/awesome-talks\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5k</span></span></a> - a collection of awesome tech talks</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://weareallaweso.me/\">We Are All Awesome!</a> - a collection of interesting posts about speaking, preparing, motivation, etc</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://helpmeabstract.com/\">HelpMeAbstract</a> - Get feedback from veteran speakers before you submit your talk.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.irongeek.com/\">Irongeek</a> - A collection of information security talks.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordstotime.com/\">Words to Time</a> - Calculates how long a speech will take to present based on the number of words.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"license\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#license\" aria-label=\"license permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>LICENSE</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/matteofigus/awesome-speaking/blob/master/LICENSE.md\">MIT</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#awesome-speaking-awesome\">awesome-speaking <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#blog-posts\">Blog Posts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#books\">Books</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#cfp\">CFP</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#clubsorganizations\">Clubs/Organizations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#miscellaneous\">Miscellaneous</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#videos\">Videos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#websites\">Websites</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#license\">LICENSE</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"awesome-speaking-awesome","value":"awesome-speaking Awesome","depth":1},{"id":"blog-posts",